Build / System Info
This was confirmed with two independent, automated browser tests (not a one-off manual check) — one in JavaScript, one in Python, both using Playwright. Each test completes onboarding, opens the Housing task, reads the actual URL behind "Official Application Portal," and asserts it belongs to a government domain. Both assertions fail as of the date above, confirming the bug is present in production. Anyone can re-run these tests at any time to check whether it has since been fixed.
